descriptionHtml:
Thranduil now in Skyrim.He is  High Elf with own hair , textures of face , brows and eyes. 
fighting style-one handed
the possibility of marriage-yes
outfit-elven armor
weapon-elven sword
compatible with UFO,AFT,EFF

Thranduil will have the body that you use in the game
You can find him in Solitude (Blue Palace).
